data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Papillion NE! The main floor features a versatile bedroom that could easily double as a home office. The family room is complete with a cozy fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for family gatherings or quiet evenings. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, showcasing an oversized island, custom-built drawers, & a walk-in pantry for ample storage. Upstairs you'll discover 2 additional bedrooms & a luxurious primary suite. The primary suite is a true retreat, featuring a sitting room, spa-like bathroom, & an expansive walk-in closet. Plus, a dedicated office space ensures productivity & privacy. The basement is an entertainer's paradise w/ a wine cellar & a custom wet bar & plenty of leisure space. It opens to a large private backyard, including a covered patio & firepit. This top-of-the-line home has no back neighbors & is close to the lake & walking trails. Enjoy the luxuries this home offers!
